## How to Sync

Simplest: redeploy from the cocapn-ai-web GitHub Pages source:
```
git pull https://github.com/SuperInstance/cocapn-ai-web.git master
```
Then copy index.html, demo-narrows.html, errata.html, and any demo-*.html files to your superinstance.ai/demos path.

Or if you're serving it differently, just update index.html from the repo.

The cocapn-ai-web repo is the canonical source for all landing page content going forward.

## Also Note

All 10 ecosystem repos now have an "Eisenstein Ecosystem" cross-reference table in their READMEs. If you mirror any of these, make sure the updated READMEs propagate.

